        "content": [
          "Demonstrates practical application of learned methodologies to successfully fulfill a leadership role for a stage production.",
          "Demonstrate proficiency in technical, managerial and leadership skills required to attain professional, entry-level positions in the live entertainment industry.",
          "Demonstrate the ability to effectively communicate ideas, concepts and outcomes through the build, load in, tech and performance of a stage production.",
